  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "merchant token",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text": " associates a payment card, merchant, and user. Apple Pay issues a merchant token when a customer initiates a purchase using Apple Pay in your app or on your website. When your app or website creates a payment request for a recurring payment or an automatic-reload payment, you pass your server’s notification URL in the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "tokenNotificationURL",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " parameter. When a life-cycle event affects the token — for example, the card’s expiration date changes, or the user or issuer deletes the token — Apple Pay sends you a notification with a unique event identifier to that ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "tokenNotificationURL",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Implement the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/MerchantTokenNotificationServices/Send-Merchant-Token-Event",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " endpoint at the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "tokenNotificationURL",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " you provide to receive and handle merchant token updates from Apple Pay.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Configure-your-server-for-Apple-Pays-requirements",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Configure your server for Apple Pay’s requirements",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To incorporate Apple Pay, your server needs to adhere to the following requirements.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "HTTPS support",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "A valid SSL certificate",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Support for the Transport Layer Security (TLS) 1.2 protocol, and at least one of the required cipher suites",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "A strict allow list for Apple Pay IP addresses for merchant validation",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "A strict allow list for Apple IP addresses for domain verification",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For more information about meeting these requirements for your server, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/apple_pay_on_the_web/setting_up_your_server",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Create-allow-lists",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Create allow lists",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For inbound merchant token notifications from Apple, allow the following IP addresses:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "code": "17.58.0.0/18",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "code": "17.58.192.0/18",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For merchant token event endpoints, allow the following URLs and IP addresses:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
